WEBVTT

00:09.351 --> 00:15.210
(Accumulate Merit and Virtue)

00:15.211 --> 00:16.381
The abbot said

00:16.771 --> 00:18.901
that you're welcome to pray

00:19.331 --> 00:20.901
and offer incense to Buddha,

00:21.491 --> 00:23.191
but if you're here
to ask about the past,

00:23.761 --> 00:25.671
the abbot refuses to speak,

00:26.171 --> 00:28.471
so you should stop
wasting your energy here.

00:36.091 --> 00:38.301
What a fool you were!

00:39.491 --> 00:43.600
What a fool you were!

00:43.601 --> 00:44.741
Mo.

00:52.961 --> 00:55.341
I just discovered that Father
was keeping a mistress here.

00:59.411 --> 01:01.071
This is none of your business!

01:01.731 --> 01:02.981
Father!

01:03.001 --> 01:04.191
I know you're upset.

01:04.321 --> 01:05.631
You can vent it out on me.

01:05.641 --> 01:07.730
There's too much misunderstanding
between you and Brother.

01:07.731 --> 01:09.450
I don't want your hatred to grow deeper.

01:09.451 --> 01:10.840
I can be the bad guy.

01:10.841 --> 01:11.981
For this family's sake.

01:14.041 --> 01:15.181
You!

01:19.241 --> 01:20.381
Your Lordship!

01:21.841 --> 01:24.391
Your Lordship, we found this
inside the woman's house.

01:30.371 --> 01:32.240
I wanted to wear
a decorative knot on my belt,

01:32.241 --> 01:33.671
so I got my maid to make one,

01:33.841 --> 01:34.960
but it turned out ugly,

01:34.961 --> 01:36.111
so I burned it.

01:39.931 --> 01:41.391
The decorative knot you burned

01:42.171 --> 01:43.541
was from this woman.

01:44.531 --> 01:45.671
It was Father.

01:46.041 --> 01:47.871
He brought me here
to learn to play the flute,

01:47.961 --> 01:49.591
and she gave me this knot.

01:50.571 --> 01:52.240
I was burning it
when you saw me that day.

01:52.241 --> 01:53.951
I didn't mean to lie...

01:55.601 --> 01:56.570
Mo.

01:56.571 --> 01:57.901
You're good at reading faces.

01:58.371 --> 02:00.391
You must know
that I wasn't lying just now.

02:02.931 --> 02:04.071
I have always

02:05.011 --> 02:07.031
respected you since young.

02:07.171 --> 02:09.341
Every family has its
own dirty laundry, right?

02:09.601 --> 02:10.480
I don't understand

02:10.481 --> 02:12.130
why all of you have to

02:12.131 --> 02:13.600
hang our dirty laundry outside?

02:13.601 --> 02:15.191
The Duke of Ying's Residence

02:15.971 --> 02:18.271
has more than just dirty laundry.

02:24.361 --> 02:26.381
You think I can't investigate further

02:27.691 --> 02:29.341
just because this woman is dead?

02:29.641 --> 02:31.871
You think I can assume
nothing has happened,

02:32.661 --> 02:34.031
and that I can reconcile with him?

02:34.631 --> 02:36.341
He's our father, after all.

02:39.891 --> 02:40.970
Men.

02:40.971 --> 02:42.751
Take Second Young Master
back to Yizhi Hall.

02:43.081 --> 02:44.311
- Take him away.
- Brother.

02:45.291 --> 02:46.431
Mo.

02:48.081 --> 02:49.221
I...

02:50.291 --> 02:51.290
Move!

02:51.291 --> 02:52.431
- Mo!
- Come on!

02:52.521 --> 02:53.661
Mo.

02:54.641 --> 02:57.061
You and Mother
were married for 20 years,

02:57.601 --> 03:00.471
and you didn't shed
a tear when she died.

03:01.641 --> 03:03.991
So, it's because
your heart was elsewhere.

03:05.171 --> 03:06.290
That makes sense.

03:06.291 --> 03:07.941
You're selfish and timid.

03:08.301 --> 03:10.271
You wouldn't hide
the daughter of a criminal here

03:10.571 --> 03:12.941
if you didn't really love her.

03:23.461 --> 03:25.271
So what if she's the daughter
of a criminal?

03:25.731 --> 03:27.260
I met someone I loved,

03:27.261 --> 03:28.690
and all I did was keep her here.

03:28.691 --> 03:30.410
I don't need my son

03:30.411 --> 03:32.101
to lecture me!

03:32.251 --> 03:34.381
I feel so bad for my mother.

05:04.351 --> 05:08.550
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

05:08.551 --> 05:11.811
=Episode 25=

05:18.161 --> 05:20.141
Fate and destiny are predestined,

05:20.721 --> 05:21.941
yet you refused to accept it.

05:26.131 --> 05:28.381
Please tell the abbot

05:28.571 --> 05:30.061
that I, Ji Yong, requests an audience.

05:33.911 --> 05:37.400
(Accumulate Merit and Virtue)

05:37.401 --> 05:38.551
The abbot asks you this.

05:39.131 --> 05:40.690
Years ago, Emperor Taizong

05:40.691 --> 05:44.061
launched a bloodbath in the capital
to obtain the throne.

05:44.611 --> 05:46.701
After that, he built this temple

05:47.131 --> 05:48.871
to appease the victims' souls.

05:49.321 --> 05:50.551
In the eyes of the public,

05:50.561 --> 05:52.461
this was for the benefit
for future generations.

05:52.521 --> 05:53.661
What do you think?

05:55.081 --> 05:58.501
Emperor Taizong
did so to relieve his guilt.

05:59.021 --> 06:02.211
No matter his intentions back then,

06:04.051 --> 06:06.551
the emperor did something good
for the people.

06:07.081 --> 06:09.871
A century has passed since then.

06:10.081 --> 06:11.311
Why should the people today

06:12.081 --> 06:15.261
continue debating about his intentions?

06:16.281 --> 06:17.671
So, you mean that

06:18.001 --> 06:19.871
just because Li Yaoniang
had been praying here

06:20.011 --> 06:22.080
over the past decade or so,

06:22.081 --> 06:24.581
the past deserves to be buried?

06:24.931 --> 06:28.061
Ms. Li decided to hide
her secrets in this temple

06:29.001 --> 06:31.021
because she didn't want
to cause any more killing.

06:31.371 --> 06:34.261
Just like Ms. Dou here,
she had kind intentions.

06:34.411 --> 06:36.881
Now that you know the truth
can harm yourself and other people,

06:37.011 --> 06:39.581
it's best not to ask about the past.

06:39.891 --> 06:44.191
As is said, "Reward will not befall
those who are intentionally kind,

06:44.661 --> 06:47.311
and punishment will not befall
those who are unintentionally evil."

06:47.571 --> 06:50.261
As you said earlier,
intentions do matter.

06:50.761 --> 06:54.111
Emperor Taizong was brave enough
to admit his mistakes

06:54.371 --> 06:56.231
and build this temple
to apologize to the dead.

06:56.851 --> 06:58.431
His intention was to redeem himself,

06:58.611 --> 07:00.621
and he worked hard
to restore peace and prosperity.

07:01.721 --> 07:03.351
However, if someone decides

07:03.371 --> 07:06.501
to bury the truth
under the pretense of regret,

07:07.051 --> 07:10.061
subsequently hurting those
who are innocent,

07:10.521 --> 07:12.751
how is that fair?

07:19.251 --> 07:20.250
Your Lordship.

07:20.251 --> 07:22.161
We have seized control
of the entire residence.

07:22.641 --> 07:24.010
You should let Shengtian Court

07:24.011 --> 07:26.621
or the Ministry of Justice
investigate the death of Ms. Li.

07:26.661 --> 07:28.991
It's inappropriate to imprison
both of them in Yizhi Hall.

07:29.081 --> 07:30.400
Your eldest uncle and third uncle

07:30.401 --> 07:31.911
has already left for the palace.

07:33.961 --> 07:35.671
That's fast.

07:36.161 --> 07:37.671
It shows that I do have to take

07:37.811 --> 07:40.200
extreme measures to discover the truth.

07:40.201 --> 07:41.751
If the palace officials are here,

07:42.401 --> 07:44.111
they can be my witness.

07:48.371 --> 07:49.821
Eighteen years ago,

07:50.521 --> 07:52.751
both Li Yaoniang and my mother
were pregnant.

07:53.401 --> 07:55.061
Li Yaoniang often visited Wanfo Temple.

07:55.321 --> 07:56.610
Coincidentally,

07:56.611 --> 07:59.351
my mother got startled there
and had a premature birth.

08:01.051 --> 08:03.791
Li Yaoniang is Song Han's mother,

08:04.251 --> 08:05.391
am I right?

08:07.161 --> 08:08.871
You're crazy.

08:09.721 --> 08:11.751
You're spouting nonsense.

08:11.891 --> 08:14.231
It's clearly written in the records

08:14.401 --> 08:16.751
that Li Yaoniang was born
to an official in Futing.

08:16.761 --> 08:19.501
Back then, you were leading
a troop of soldiers in Futing.

08:20.011 --> 08:21.791
Her entire family
was thrown into prison,

08:22.131 --> 08:24.501
and the records showed
that you visited her twice.

08:24.611 --> 08:26.320
If she weren't Song Han's birth mother,

08:26.321 --> 08:28.791
why would she have
the same kind of decorative knot?

08:29.891 --> 08:32.311
You've had an affair with her.

08:37.561 --> 08:38.701
Song Mo.

08:40.761 --> 08:42.701
You're just scared that Han

08:42.731 --> 08:44.981
would steal your position.

08:45.211 --> 08:47.741
How could you incriminate him?

08:48.281 --> 08:49.551
Don't forget

08:49.891 --> 08:52.151
that he's your brother!

08:52.161 --> 08:54.341
How could you say that
in front of your mother?

08:54.351 --> 08:56.010
(Virtuous Wife,
Madam Jiang's Memorial Tablet)

08:56.011 --> 08:58.861
Don't you feel any shame

09:00.131 --> 09:02.271
lying in front of my mother?

09:05.731 --> 09:08.061
Ms. Dou, you are right.

09:08.761 --> 09:10.551
However, today's events

09:10.681 --> 09:13.461
weren't the results
of Li Yaoniang's intentions.

09:22.761 --> 09:23.941
One's opinions

09:24.401 --> 09:25.911
might not reflect those of others.

09:26.681 --> 09:28.440
Your standard of interpreting intentions

09:28.441 --> 09:29.861
may be different from mine,

09:30.391 --> 09:32.941
but this doesn't deny the fact
that we all have good intentions.

09:34.611 --> 09:37.341
Please tell us the truth, Abbot,

09:37.491 --> 09:39.151
so as to bring justice to both families.

09:49.891 --> 09:51.741
If you insist, Ms. Dou.

09:51.891 --> 09:56.031
Perhaps you're fated
to resolve this turbulent past.

09:57.011 --> 10:00.061
Eighteen years ago,
on the day of Jingzhe,

10:00.521 --> 10:04.311
both Ms. Li and Madam Jiang
were at this temple.

10:04.891 --> 10:08.370
Back then, Ms. Li carried
a one-month-old baby

10:08.371 --> 10:10.461
in her arms,

10:11.131 --> 10:14.031
and she wanted to pray for the baby.

10:14.131 --> 10:17.941
As for Madam Jiang, the Duchess of Ying,
she had a premature birth here.

10:18.161 --> 10:22.151
The Duke of Ying said
she gave birth to a baby boy,

10:22.891 --> 10:26.631
but I saw clearly

10:27.521 --> 10:31.031
that she gave birth to a baby girl.

10:36.231 --> 10:37.280
(Virtuous Wife,
Madam Jiang's Memorial Tablet)

10:37.281 --> 10:38.421
Father.

10:39.041 --> 10:40.920
Am I really not my mother's real son?

10:40.921 --> 10:42.061
Ridiculous!

10:42.611 --> 10:45.560
Our family records clearly state
that Han is Huisun's son!

10:45.561 --> 10:47.791
A mere decorative knot

10:48.131 --> 10:50.031
cannot upend the truth!

10:51.401 --> 10:53.221
Then, have you heard of

10:53.731 --> 10:55.741
a maternity test?

10:56.561 --> 10:59.511
You drip the blood of a child
onto a parent's bone

10:59.891 --> 11:01.511
and see whether the blood seeps in

11:01.561 --> 11:04.151
to determine
if they're related by blood.

11:12.491 --> 11:14.671
Huisun has already been buried.

11:15.251 --> 11:16.730
You dare to dig her grave?

11:16.731 --> 11:19.061
You're not qualified enough
to dig my mother's grave!

11:19.641 --> 11:20.781
Bring her in!

11:29.491 --> 11:30.821
Don't touch her!

11:31.211 --> 11:32.461
Where should we cut?

11:32.891 --> 11:33.760
The skull?

11:33.761 --> 11:35.160
Don't touch her!

11:35.161 --> 11:36.520
Or the leg bone?

11:36.521 --> 11:38.341
Don't touch her!

11:40.161 --> 11:42.151
She has the beautiful hands

11:42.801 --> 11:44.311
of a musician.

11:45.681 --> 11:46.821
You dare?

11:49.641 --> 11:51.101
Why not?

11:52.331 --> 11:53.230
Hold it!

11:53.231 --> 11:54.250
(Loyalty)

11:54.251 --> 11:56.151
I did not let your mother down.

11:56.251 --> 11:59.431
The only person
I have ever let down is her!

12:15.041 --> 12:18.911
Li Yaoniang was her stage name
given by the music office.

12:19.371 --> 12:22.631
She is Li Shuyao, the daughter
of Futing's Magistrate.

12:23.441 --> 12:27.271
Back then, I was just a lowborn
deployed to Futing.

12:28.801 --> 12:33.031
I met her at the seaside in Futing.

12:35.211 --> 12:38.791
I was playing the sheng,
and she played the flute.

12:39.251 --> 12:41.791
We played in harmony

12:42.801 --> 12:45.031
and promised to stay together.

12:46.681 --> 12:49.391
But Jiang Meisun

12:49.801 --> 12:52.791
ruined everything!

12:53.371 --> 12:56.031
He raided the Lis' residence

12:56.041 --> 12:59.341
and ruined Shuyao's life!

13:01.891 --> 13:04.631
Then, as fate would have it,

13:05.211 --> 13:06.551
His Majesty

13:06.611 --> 13:10.741
ordered me to marry
the sister of my enemy.

13:11.161 --> 13:12.981
Everything I had wanted for years,

13:13.161 --> 13:15.890
status, career, and wealth

13:15.891 --> 13:18.800
were got overnight.

13:18.801 --> 13:22.911
But later, I met her again
in the Music Office.

13:25.331 --> 13:29.221
We had a child.

13:33.271 --> 13:34.581
I checked the magistrate records.

13:35.211 --> 13:37.461
The Li family was incarcerated
because of corruption.

13:38.011 --> 13:40.431
The proceedings
were legal and reasonable.

13:40.561 --> 13:43.511
You think you let her down.

13:45.041 --> 13:46.511
What about my mother?

13:49.731 --> 13:51.631
Even when she died,

13:52.371 --> 13:55.311
she had never held
her real child in her arms.

14:00.131 --> 14:01.581
Where is the child now?

14:07.491 --> 14:08.631
Speak!

14:11.331 --> 14:13.271
That child is already dead.

14:13.681 --> 14:15.920
The Jiangs owe me this!

14:15.921 --> 14:18.610
If Jiang Meisun didn't
raid the Lis' residence,

14:18.611 --> 14:21.221
I wouldn't be in this state now!

14:21.331 --> 14:25.271
Han should have been my heir apparent!

14:26.841 --> 14:28.210
My uncle enforced the law justly.

14:28.211 --> 14:29.681
My mother treated you wholeheartedly.

14:29.691 --> 14:31.271
You owe them two lives!

14:31.681 --> 14:32.821
No,

14:33.211 --> 14:34.351
three lives!

14:34.501 --> 14:35.610
Mo!

14:35.611 --> 14:36.920
Father said that out of anger.

14:36.921 --> 14:38.741
You're still his son.

14:39.011 --> 14:41.330
Moreover, His Majesty said

14:41.331 --> 14:43.061
that both of you are...

14:43.441 --> 14:45.511
If you have a shred of conscience left,

14:45.521 --> 14:46.701
tell me the truth.

14:46.921 --> 14:47.760
Who helped you

14:47.761 --> 14:50.221
rescue Li Yaoniang
from the Music Office?

14:50.251 --> 14:51.821
There's no such person!

14:51.971 --> 14:53.221
You're still lying!

14:53.441 --> 14:56.311
You snuck a court performer out
and hid her in the capital for years.

14:56.321 --> 14:58.811
It's impossible if you got no help
from high-ranking officials.

15:00.281 --> 15:02.631
Eventually, my mother
discovered her presence.

15:03.011 --> 15:04.861
That's why you killed her.

15:04.921 --> 15:06.741
Your mother was my wife.

15:06.891 --> 15:08.821
Why would I kill her?

15:08.971 --> 15:10.680
She died of illness!

15:10.681 --> 15:12.271
If you didn't intend this,

15:12.331 --> 15:14.610
then you must have
been ordered to do so.

15:14.611 --> 15:16.271
Those people killed my uncle

15:16.491 --> 15:18.490
and wanted to eliminate the Jiangs,

15:18.491 --> 15:19.490
right?

15:19.491 --> 15:21.271
You're spouting nonsense.

15:21.441 --> 15:24.341
Revenge has driven you crazy!

15:27.891 --> 15:29.271
You're right.

15:34.091 --> 15:35.231
Bring the evidence.

15:44.871 --> 15:46.821
Licorice candied fruits.

15:46.891 --> 15:49.511
These are not meant to be taken
with my mother's prescription.

15:49.971 --> 15:51.520
You bought these fruits.

15:51.521 --> 15:54.101
You were the one
who made her die from illness!

15:55.441 --> 15:56.850
I'm not a physician.

15:56.851 --> 15:59.941
How would I know
these foods are contradictory?

15:59.971 --> 16:01.850
These are just candies.

16:01.851 --> 16:03.400
As the master of the household,

16:03.401 --> 16:05.511
why would I care about mere candies?

16:06.881 --> 16:07.760
You won't confess?

16:07.761 --> 16:09.061
I have nothing to confess!

16:12.251 --> 16:13.391
You see that?

16:13.681 --> 16:15.031
He forced me to do so.

16:16.281 --> 16:17.741
Take him to the main hall!

16:17.751 --> 16:18.800
- Yes, Your Lordship!
- Mo.

16:18.801 --> 16:19.640
You...

16:19.641 --> 16:20.920
- Mo!
- You!

16:20.921 --> 16:22.061
Move it!

16:24.731 --> 16:26.001
This is an old case that involves

16:26.011 --> 16:27.800
the private affairs
of a prestigious family.

16:27.801 --> 16:29.890
Your interference would only
create more resentment.

16:29.891 --> 16:31.631
Why don't you stay
in your residence first?

16:31.921 --> 16:33.151
I'll brew a pot of tea,

16:33.161 --> 16:35.101
and we can discuss our next step.

16:36.561 --> 16:39.551
(Yantang is blinded by hatred now.)

16:39.971 --> 16:41.551
(Song Yichun is in danger.)

16:42.091 --> 16:43.490
(I have to stop him now.)

16:43.491 --> 16:44.560
(Song Mo, Star of Death)

16:44.561 --> 16:46.631
(In a fit of hatred, he began killing)

16:46.731 --> 16:48.850
(to take his revenge.)

16:48.851 --> 16:51.191
(Song Mo's hair turned white
after killing his father and brother.)

16:51.211 --> 16:54.221
(Perhaps it was Li Yaoniang's death
that started it all?)

16:59.851 --> 17:01.741
What's done is done.

17:01.801 --> 17:03.400
Even if you try to stop it now,

17:03.401 --> 17:06.071
you can only change things temporarily,
but not forever.

17:06.331 --> 17:08.200
My strength may be minuscule,

17:08.201 --> 17:09.871
and I may not alter my destiny,

17:10.201 --> 17:12.021
but I'll walk alongside him.

17:25.481 --> 17:29.151
Mantis Song is a lucky guy, indeed.

17:31.131 --> 17:32.541
Mo!

17:32.921 --> 17:33.920
All I know

17:33.921 --> 17:35.871
is that my mother is Jiang Huisun,

17:36.241 --> 17:37.810
and Song Yichun is our father.

17:37.811 --> 17:39.431
You're my most respected brother.

17:39.891 --> 17:42.431
This family is what I identify with.

17:43.091 --> 17:44.570
You're still pleading for him.

17:44.571 --> 17:46.261
I'm doing this for you.

17:46.421 --> 17:47.601
If you do hate me,

17:48.331 --> 17:49.330
I can kill myself now.

17:49.331 --> 17:50.471
I won't blame you for it.

17:54.771 --> 17:56.631
If you truly see me as your brother,

17:57.131 --> 17:58.541
then tell me,

17:59.201 --> 18:01.261
when did you realize the truth?

18:02.571 --> 18:03.711
Today.

18:04.771 --> 18:06.331
I did feel that things were strange,

18:06.921 --> 18:08.191
but now that Mother is gone,

18:09.011 --> 18:10.461
I was scared that you'd abandon me,

18:11.301 --> 18:13.161
so I pretended that nothing happened.

18:18.161 --> 18:19.781
Mo, please stop!

18:19.961 --> 18:21.101
I beg you.

18:22.291 --> 18:23.431
Remember this?

18:25.331 --> 18:28.591
You gave me this blade
and said you'd let me join you someday.

18:29.201 --> 18:30.981
We confiscated this blade from pirates.

18:31.161 --> 18:32.301
It's yours now.

18:33.291 --> 18:34.370
Thank you.

18:34.371 --> 18:35.611
I know you love grilled venison,

18:35.621 --> 18:37.781
so I'm planning to hunt a deer tomorrow.

18:38.331 --> 18:39.370
Sure.

18:39.371 --> 18:40.981
If you manage to hunt one,

18:41.051 --> 18:42.671
I will ask Father

18:42.721 --> 18:45.191
to assign a position for you in Futing.

18:45.291 --> 18:47.111
It's a deal. Don't break your promise.

18:47.901 --> 18:49.240
Back then, Mother was still alive.

18:49.241 --> 18:50.541
Don't you mention her!

18:51.761 --> 18:53.781
Our uncle died before he could return.

18:53.961 --> 18:55.981
Mother was betrayed and insulted.

18:56.441 --> 18:58.431
If I can't even protect my family,

18:58.551 --> 19:00.431
how could I call myself a son?

19:01.051 --> 19:04.221
Now, even if everyone disagrees with me,

19:04.961 --> 19:07.440
I will restore justice.

19:07.441 --> 19:08.581
Mo.

19:09.721 --> 19:11.461
Please let go of Father

19:11.961 --> 19:13.111
for my sake.

19:21.811 --> 19:23.671
If you still see me as your brother,

19:25.051 --> 19:26.351
return to Xixiang Place now.

19:26.991 --> 19:28.370
- Take him away.
- Yes, Your Lordship!

19:28.371 --> 19:29.511
Mo.

19:29.611 --> 19:30.751
Mo!

19:31.131 --> 19:32.271
Mo!

19:32.531 --> 19:33.671
Mo!

19:45.961 --> 19:47.101
Let go of me!

19:49.961 --> 19:51.570
I am the Duke of Ying!

19:51.571 --> 19:53.330
The emperor will decide who's wrong!

19:53.331 --> 19:54.890
You cannot punish me!

19:54.891 --> 19:55.890
Fine.

19:55.891 --> 19:57.200
As long as you tell me

19:57.201 --> 19:59.071
who's behind all this.

20:01.001 --> 20:03.071
So, that's what you want to know?

20:04.001 --> 20:05.141
Sure.

20:05.291 --> 20:06.461
Burn me, then.

20:16.531 --> 20:18.981
Even the heavens are on my side!

20:19.291 --> 20:21.640
If your mother were still alive,

20:21.641 --> 20:23.530
she'd stop you from doing so!

20:23.531 --> 20:25.000
How dare you still mention her?

20:25.001 --> 20:27.981
I have always loved only Shuyao.

20:28.161 --> 20:30.871
I married Jiang Huisun
only for status and wealth!

20:31.091 --> 20:33.261
Having you with her

20:33.401 --> 20:36.301
is the biggest regret of my life!

20:39.481 --> 20:40.480
Your Lordship!

20:40.481 --> 20:41.621
Your Lordship!

20:41.921 --> 20:43.701
You can't even hold your blade firmly.

20:43.721 --> 20:45.530
Don't you feel more painful

20:45.531 --> 20:47.261
the more you feel angry?

20:49.441 --> 20:50.741
I'm poisoned.

20:51.531 --> 20:53.461
When did you poison me?

20:55.131 --> 20:56.430
When did you grow

20:56.431 --> 20:59.151
your first strand of white hair?

21:00.091 --> 21:02.960
That day, I punished you
only to warn you,

21:02.961 --> 21:05.330
but Lyu Zheng poisoned you
without my knowledge.

21:05.331 --> 21:06.850
You will never have to know

21:06.851 --> 21:08.640
who's behind this.

21:08.641 --> 21:10.501
There's poison on the beating sticks?

21:10.721 --> 21:13.920
When the poison seeps into your bones,

21:13.921 --> 21:15.501
your hair will turn completely white,

21:16.811 --> 21:19.451
and your life will come to an end.

21:23.051 --> 21:24.191
Yantang!

21:24.371 --> 21:25.591
Stop that!

21:27.481 --> 21:28.480
Yantang.

21:28.481 --> 21:29.741
Don't be rash.

21:31.681 --> 21:34.911
I once promised you
that I will protect you.

21:35.641 --> 21:37.981
Now, I realize that I've been
living in a lie,

21:38.401 --> 21:40.191
and I can't even protect my family.

21:40.891 --> 21:42.261
That's not it.

21:42.921 --> 21:44.541
You can't turn to the dark side

21:44.611 --> 21:45.751
just because fate is cruel.

21:45.811 --> 21:47.351
If the heavens refuses to be fair,

21:47.531 --> 21:48.770
I will restore justice myself!

21:48.771 --> 21:49.941
Come on!

21:54.811 --> 21:58.541
No matter how difficult and tough
the road ahead is,

21:59.241 --> 22:01.151
I will walk alongside you.

22:06.721 --> 22:07.861
Yantang!

22:09.091 --> 22:10.261
Yantang!

22:12.161 --> 22:13.301
Yantang!

22:14.811 --> 22:16.981
Imperial Decree!

22:17.681 --> 22:19.911
His Majesty has decreed

22:20.441 --> 22:24.680
that the Duke of Ying
and his son enter the palace now!

22:24.681 --> 22:26.261
Kill me!

22:26.481 --> 22:27.920
If you kill me,

22:27.921 --> 22:30.981
you'll be defying His Majesty's orders!

22:35.961 --> 22:37.541
His Majesty has also decreed

22:37.681 --> 22:41.111
that you will receive treatment
in the palace if you are ill or injured.

22:41.811 --> 22:42.951
Your Lordship!

22:47.331 --> 22:48.471
Yantang!

22:49.161 --> 22:50.240
Yantang!

22:50.241 --> 22:51.130
- Yantang!
- Madam

22:51.131 --> 22:52.911
is not called upon.

22:52.921 --> 22:54.191
You shall stay here.

22:57.201 --> 22:58.341
Your Ladyship!

22:59.201 --> 23:00.591
Yantang!

23:05.571 --> 23:06.711
Your Majesty.

23:06.921 --> 23:09.891
Lord Song is afflicted
with the poison of hatred.

23:10.001 --> 23:12.391
This is a very rare poison

23:12.721 --> 23:16.610
that doesn't show any initial symptoms,

23:16.611 --> 23:18.671
but when the victim's hair turns white,

23:19.051 --> 23:21.090
that's when the poison takes effect.

23:21.091 --> 23:22.591
It can cause immense pain.

23:22.991 --> 23:24.831
When the victim's hair
turns completely white,

23:25.571 --> 23:27.151
he will die soon.

23:31.481 --> 23:33.671
He's still so young.

23:38.641 --> 23:40.391
How do you cure it?

23:40.771 --> 23:42.501
As its name suggests,

23:42.571 --> 23:44.330
if he can let go of his hatred,

23:44.331 --> 23:45.941
his pain will be relieved.

23:46.481 --> 23:50.741
However, given Lord Song's
current condition,

23:51.051 --> 23:53.741
even with our best medicine,
he can only live

23:54.291 --> 23:55.831
up to a year.

24:09.431 --> 24:11.400
(Yuxi Palace)
Your Majesty!

24:11.401 --> 24:12.610
When the poison takes effect,

24:12.611 --> 24:14.570
the victim may turn violent.

24:14.571 --> 24:15.850
Please consider your safety.

24:15.851 --> 24:17.890
Don't go, Your Majesty!

24:17.891 --> 24:19.031
Your Majesty!

24:19.611 --> 24:21.831
I want him to live.

24:22.681 --> 24:25.301
If you can't find an antidote in a year

24:25.681 --> 24:26.821
and he dies,

24:27.441 --> 24:28.871
you'll be joining him.

24:29.811 --> 24:31.431
Yes, Your Majesty.

24:32.201 --> 24:35.021
If word of Lord Song's illness spreads,

24:35.331 --> 24:37.050
you know what will happen.

24:37.051 --> 24:38.741
Yes, I understand.

24:46.721 --> 24:47.871
Uncle.

24:48.441 --> 24:50.591
I will not let that woman
enter our house.

24:50.811 --> 24:53.221
It was him who switched Mother's child.

24:54.371 --> 24:56.021
There must be someone behind him.

24:56.331 --> 24:57.591
I have to find out.

24:57.811 --> 24:58.920
I have to...

24:58.921 --> 24:59.960
Yantang.

24:59.961 --> 25:01.591
Uncle, Uncle.

25:02.371 --> 25:03.631
I have failed

25:03.871 --> 25:05.431
to protect my mother.

25:05.961 --> 25:07.351
Please punish me.

25:07.391 --> 25:08.330
Blame me, Uncle.

25:08.331 --> 25:10.200
- Wake up, Lord Song.
- Punish me.

25:10.201 --> 25:11.781
- Uncle.
- It's His Majesty.

25:11.851 --> 25:13.391
He's the emperor.

25:14.131 --> 25:15.271
Yantang.

25:15.811 --> 25:17.261
You'll be fine.

25:18.051 --> 25:22.221
Your mother and uncle
will not die in vain.

25:24.721 --> 25:25.861
Your Majesty.

25:25.991 --> 25:28.111
About what transpired
at the Duke of Ying's residence,

25:28.531 --> 25:30.431
you have to deliver the verdict.

25:50.241 --> 25:51.671
Eunuch Wang!

25:51.681 --> 25:54.290
Eunuch Wang, spare him!

25:54.291 --> 25:56.530
Even Ms. Li has killed herself
out of guilt.

25:56.531 --> 25:58.200
We can't get the truth
out of her anymore.

25:58.201 --> 25:59.850
It's impossible to determine his sins.

25:59.851 --> 26:01.501
Eunuch Wang.

26:01.711 --> 26:04.000
My ancestors had worked
alongside the former emperor

26:04.001 --> 26:05.781
to establish this kingdom

26:05.891 --> 26:07.981
and earn our title of duke.

26:07.991 --> 26:09.970
We have retained this title
for three generations.

26:09.971 --> 26:11.720
You can't kill my brother

26:11.721 --> 26:13.200
just because he had an affair

26:13.201 --> 26:15.160
and a love child!

26:15.161 --> 26:17.591
Imperial Decree!

26:22.721 --> 26:26.720
The Duke of Ying has had an affair
and switched his children

26:26.721 --> 26:28.370
to make his love child his official son.

26:28.371 --> 26:30.221
This is an unethical act.

26:30.571 --> 26:34.770
He will be stripped off his position
in the Military Command.

26:34.771 --> 26:38.301
His title as duke will be retained,
but he will have to repent.

26:40.441 --> 26:43.781
I have committed a heinous sin.

26:44.371 --> 26:46.461
I am willing to accept punishment.

26:47.201 --> 26:51.290
However, my son Song Han
was not involved.

26:51.291 --> 26:52.831
He did not know any of this.

26:53.721 --> 26:56.021
I hope His Majesty can pardon him

26:56.241 --> 27:00.541
and let him retain
his title in the family.

27:03.721 --> 27:05.680
Decorum and honor

27:05.681 --> 27:07.351
are the pillars of the society,

27:07.961 --> 27:11.021
and social rankings
are the base of decorum.

27:11.161 --> 27:13.050
The eldest daughter of your residence

27:13.051 --> 27:14.391
is still nowhere to be found.

27:14.481 --> 27:17.461
Do you think His Majesty would bother

27:18.011 --> 27:20.461
pitying a love child?

27:38.961 --> 27:40.941
This is to relieve pain caused by anger.

27:40.961 --> 27:42.610
This is to cure colds.

27:42.611 --> 27:44.191
Don't mix them up.

27:44.571 --> 27:46.391
You must be terribly anxious

27:46.481 --> 27:48.141
to brew every
single concoction there is.

27:48.151 --> 27:50.441
Don't you think the palace physicians
can prepare them too?

27:50.451 --> 27:51.680
You got Su Lan to bring me here

27:51.681 --> 27:52.871
just to give you these herbs?

27:54.851 --> 27:55.991
Su Xin.

27:56.051 --> 27:58.071
Get more spring water.

27:58.091 --> 27:59.231
Yes, Your Ladyship.

28:02.771 --> 28:04.071
Whatever happens,

28:04.131 --> 28:05.680
the residence will only

28:05.681 --> 28:07.111
get busier.

28:07.481 --> 28:08.850
I'm counting on you

28:08.851 --> 28:10.090
and Ansu to look after

28:10.091 --> 28:11.231
Zhaowen Bookstore.

28:13.331 --> 28:15.431
All I care about is you, Dou Zhao.

28:16.331 --> 28:18.741
Stop bothering me over
Mantis Song's problems.

28:39.331 --> 28:40.941
This balm is good for healing scars.

28:41.481 --> 28:42.911
Apply this every day.

28:47.681 --> 28:49.461
Ever since you got married,

28:49.721 --> 28:50.770
your life has become

28:50.771 --> 28:52.071
utterly boring.

28:52.331 --> 28:53.501
If you want to leave,

28:53.891 --> 28:55.391
I have plenty of ideas.

28:58.771 --> 29:00.781
Since I know what's going to happen,

29:01.051 --> 29:03.221
all the more I should try to stop them.

29:04.481 --> 29:06.191
I want to follow my heart.

29:07.851 --> 29:08.991
As for the results,

29:10.531 --> 29:12.541
these are not within my considerations.

29:23.201 --> 29:24.341
Your Lordship.

29:26.571 --> 29:27.741
Don't tell my wife

29:28.811 --> 29:30.221
about my condition.

29:31.331 --> 29:34.021
If your health continues to deteriorate,

29:34.371 --> 29:36.191
do you think you can hide it from her?

29:38.051 --> 29:40.191
I wanted to protect her,

29:41.811 --> 29:42.951
but now,

29:44.611 --> 29:46.191
I'm letting her down.

29:47.681 --> 29:49.631
This case is getting more complicated.

29:49.961 --> 29:51.911
I have to resolve it soon,

29:52.441 --> 29:53.741
or else she'd have to face

29:54.051 --> 29:56.191
those monsters alone after I die.

29:57.531 --> 29:59.191
Even when I'm in the underworld,

30:00.441 --> 30:01.781
I'd still be worried.

30:07.921 --> 30:09.061
Then...

30:09.961 --> 30:12.431
What are your plans now?

30:15.051 --> 30:17.071
Give me some time alone.

30:27.371 --> 30:28.830
Pick something fresh for me.

30:28.831 --> 30:29.971
Sure.

31:06.581 --> 31:07.770
(If I can spend the last part)

31:07.771 --> 31:09.871
(of my journey with Ms. Longevity,)

31:10.721 --> 31:12.741
(my life would still be worth it.)

31:17.401 --> 31:18.541
Your Lordship.

31:19.091 --> 31:21.351
We have news from Chen Jia.

31:22.891 --> 31:23.770
Your Lordship!

31:23.771 --> 31:25.090
Spare me!

31:25.091 --> 31:28.151
I didn't know anything back then.

31:28.241 --> 31:30.741
I really didn't know!

31:31.721 --> 31:32.941
Spill the beans, now!

31:37.371 --> 31:38.511
Back then,

31:38.961 --> 31:41.391
the Duke ordered me
to take care of a baby girl.

31:41.811 --> 31:45.021
However, that baby was weak
since she was born prematurely.

31:45.051 --> 31:47.351
She died in a few days.

31:51.851 --> 31:53.431
Spare me, Your Lordship!

31:54.291 --> 31:55.911
What happened back then?

31:56.131 --> 31:57.271
Tell me, now!

31:57.921 --> 32:00.431
I only remember that the baby girl

32:01.481 --> 32:04.671
was brought from Madam Jiang's room.

32:05.121 --> 32:05.960
As for the rest,

32:05.961 --> 32:08.351
I really don't know anything!

32:11.481 --> 32:14.021
Remove him from the residence.

32:14.371 --> 32:15.511
Throw him to a military camp.

32:15.531 --> 32:16.571
Just make sure he's alive.

32:16.581 --> 32:17.400
Yes, Your Lordship.

32:17.401 --> 32:18.400
Move!

32:18.401 --> 32:21.151
Your Lordship, I was wrong!

32:21.331 --> 32:22.671
Your Lordship!

32:37.961 --> 32:39.631
I tried putting myself in your shoes.

32:39.991 --> 32:42.981
You were born to a commoner mother,
and you were restricted by your status,

32:44.141 --> 32:46.111
so you married a noblewoman
whom you didn't love.

32:47.371 --> 32:48.511
Regret

32:48.771 --> 32:50.941
became your excuse
to do whatever is necessary.

32:52.201 --> 32:53.741
The mastermind behind you...

32:54.641 --> 32:56.191
What did they promise you?

32:57.001 --> 32:58.261
Did they promise you

32:58.921 --> 33:00.541
to make Song Han a duke?

33:03.371 --> 33:07.221
You Jiangs have always been snobbish,

33:08.401 --> 33:10.191
thinking that you're

33:10.891 --> 33:13.221
saviors of the world.

33:13.571 --> 33:15.781
Now, I'm going to make myself clear.

33:15.851 --> 33:18.391
I don't need anyone
to offer me any deals.

33:20.771 --> 33:23.071
To take Ms. Li away
from the Music Office,

33:23.611 --> 33:25.541
you'd have to go through
the Ministry of Justice.

33:26.161 --> 33:27.501
There's someone behind you.

33:28.851 --> 33:30.301
I am a duke.

33:30.441 --> 33:32.701
How is it impossible for me to take away

33:32.731 --> 33:34.151
an incriminated musician?

33:34.611 --> 33:37.391
You've always been
secretly serving Liaodong.

33:38.091 --> 33:39.671
Looks like Song Han is involved too.

33:39.881 --> 33:41.070
Han has nothing to do with it!

33:41.071 --> 33:42.810
That means you're involved.

33:42.811 --> 33:43.951
Enough!

33:44.301 --> 33:45.831
When the bandits besieged the capital,

33:45.841 --> 33:47.871
you switched all the guards
in the Military Command

33:47.881 --> 33:49.011
and even the capital reserves

33:49.021 --> 33:50.330
to Lord Qing's men.

33:50.331 --> 33:51.960
There must be some palace officials

33:51.961 --> 33:53.530
and civil servants

33:53.531 --> 33:55.191
who are working for him, right?

33:55.921 --> 33:57.281
He's created such an elaborate plan

33:58.161 --> 34:00.191
not just for status,

34:00.441 --> 34:02.871
but for treason.

34:07.681 --> 34:09.151
I don't understand

34:09.961 --> 34:11.861
what you're talking about.

34:16.291 --> 34:18.111
Have you thought about Song Han?

34:18.921 --> 34:19.960
Do you think he'd be free

34:19.961 --> 34:21.901
after you die?

34:22.691 --> 34:24.551
He'd be all alone in this world.

34:25.001 --> 34:26.671
Doesn't that worry you?

34:28.001 --> 34:29.391
Han is innocent.

34:29.401 --> 34:30.881
If you dare to lay a finger on him...

34:30.891 --> 34:32.701
Even if I don't, someone else will.

34:33.531 --> 34:34.671
What?

34:34.691 --> 34:38.511
Right now, you're just a discarded pawn.

34:39.521 --> 34:42.261
Even if you carry
all your secrets to your grave,

34:42.691 --> 34:43.831
those people

34:44.651 --> 34:46.951
won't let Song Han live.

34:56.481 --> 34:58.191
Take care.

35:45.991 --> 35:51.891
(Beloved Sister, Jiang)

35:59.431 --> 36:02.811
(Beloved Sister, Jiang)

36:17.651 --> 36:19.191
How do you know I'm here?

36:22.691 --> 36:24.901
General Yan has told me everything.

36:26.331 --> 36:27.701
What did he say?

36:27.921 --> 36:30.591
About your late sister.

36:31.001 --> 36:32.080
That's why I thought

36:32.081 --> 36:33.861
you'd be here to mourn for her.

36:40.691 --> 36:43.520
The imperial physician said you fainted

36:43.521 --> 36:45.991
because you were overwhelmed by anger.

36:46.601 --> 36:49.471
This medicine should
alleviate your symptoms.

36:53.691 --> 36:55.301
Why do you look so pale?

36:57.691 --> 36:58.831
Let me take a look.

37:07.121 --> 37:08.261
Your hand...

37:08.961 --> 37:10.101
Does it still hurt?

37:13.331 --> 37:14.471
Not anymore.

37:14.691 --> 37:15.831
I'm sorry.

37:17.811 --> 37:18.991
It's my fault.

37:22.771 --> 37:26.221
You lost someone twice.

37:27.371 --> 37:29.471
That must be really upsetting.

37:36.691 --> 37:38.071
I've made you worried.

37:39.251 --> 37:40.391
You were right.

37:41.371 --> 37:43.341
If the same thing happens again,

37:43.851 --> 37:45.261
please stop me.

37:46.961 --> 37:48.821
I cannot lose control anymore.

37:50.561 --> 37:52.741
You took the words out of my mouth.

37:56.691 --> 37:59.511
Come on, drink it while it's hot.

38:07.171 --> 38:08.341
Back then,

38:08.481 --> 38:10.991
when I managed to return
to the residence alive,

38:11.601 --> 38:13.671
I thought that was the worst
I'd ever experience.

38:15.171 --> 38:16.591
Ever since I could remember,

38:17.171 --> 38:19.261
Song Yichun has always
listened to my mother.

38:19.651 --> 38:22.151
He treated her with respect.

38:22.691 --> 38:24.701
Whenever he was deployed out of town,

38:25.481 --> 38:27.781
he would return
with gifts for my mother.

38:29.521 --> 38:31.551
I thought it was out of love,

38:32.811 --> 38:34.261
but it was actually tolerance.

38:35.171 --> 38:36.311
It was hatred.

38:39.651 --> 38:40.791
I don't know

38:42.651 --> 38:44.631
what's real in my life anymore.

38:47.211 --> 38:48.901
Your mother's love for you,

38:49.651 --> 38:51.631
your uncle's guidance,

38:52.121 --> 38:54.511
and your army's undying loyalty

38:55.171 --> 38:56.381
are all real.

38:58.561 --> 38:59.701
I'm real, too.

39:07.921 --> 39:09.071
With how things are now,

39:10.561 --> 39:12.301
I shouldn't let you
get involved in my pain.

39:13.991 --> 39:16.341
As a couple, we should stay
together through thick and thin

39:16.691 --> 39:17.861
and share our joys and woes.

39:19.081 --> 39:20.221
From now on,

39:20.251 --> 39:22.890
you can dump all your unhappiness

39:22.891 --> 39:24.421
and troubles on me.

39:25.441 --> 39:29.341
We are different from your parents.

39:38.961 --> 39:40.101
Yantang.

39:41.001 --> 39:42.741
Let me offer some
incense to your sister.

39:43.371 --> 39:44.951
Then, let's go home.

39:47.691 --> 39:48.831
Sure.

39:56.331 --> 39:57.671
Look, fireworks!

39:58.001 --> 39:59.141
So pretty.

40:00.391 --> 40:03.420
♪I want to hide like the moon♪

40:03.421 --> 40:07.131
♪Like a butterfly drawn to flowers♪

40:07.201 --> 40:13.701
♪Like ink drops fading into my heart
that turns to longing♪

40:14.081 --> 40:15.341
Do you remember

40:15.961 --> 40:19.341
we saw fireworks together
for the first time outside the prison?

40:21.731 --> 40:23.511
Back then, Dou Shishu and his followers

40:23.521 --> 40:24.991
kept trying to impeach me,

40:25.651 --> 40:27.741
and you called upon Gu Yu to protect me.

40:28.481 --> 40:30.111
Why did you do so?

40:30.791 --> 40:33.991
Even fireworks come in
a multitude of colors.

40:34.921 --> 40:37.511
He and I are different.

40:40.521 --> 40:41.861
Back then, I thought

40:42.251 --> 40:44.991
that if this woman
could be my strategist,

40:45.601 --> 40:47.341
I'd have nothing to fear.

40:47.961 --> 40:49.511
So,

40:49.651 --> 40:51.991
is that why you locked
Mr. Chen up for so long?

40:53.961 --> 40:55.901
You're just as ruthless, my wife.

40:56.481 --> 40:58.901
You locked General Yan up
in the coal room.

40:58.961 --> 40:59.810
When I found him,

40:59.811 --> 41:01.650
he was covered in soot.

41:01.651 --> 41:07.661
♪Seeing the full moon
even at the end of the world♪

41:11.521 --> 41:14.671
Time fleets in a blink of an eye.

41:15.851 --> 41:17.221
Beautiful things

41:18.171 --> 41:19.701
never last.

41:20.371 --> 41:21.671
You can't hold them.

41:41.211 --> 41:43.151
Beautiful things may not last long,

41:43.771 --> 41:45.191
but you can hold them.

42:15.211 --> 42:17.031
You may be my strategist,

42:17.041 --> 42:18.341
but I only want you

42:18.961 --> 42:21.191
to relax and be my wife.

42:54.391 --> 42:55.730
I'm willing to stay by your side.

42:55.731 --> 42:57.071
I'll have no regrets.

42:57.691 --> 42:58.730
I used to think

42:58.731 --> 43:00.701
that I could protect you,

43:01.891 --> 43:03.221
but now,

43:03.891 --> 43:05.000
I can't do it anymore.

43:05.001 --> 43:09.331
♪Forsaking words of farewell♪

43:10.101 --> 43:12.771
♪The golden fiery steed
rides across the vast horizon♪

43:13.381 --> 43:16.481
♪In this life, oh♪

43:16.631 --> 43:18.310
♪Without you♪

43:18.311 --> 43:21.931
♪What is there to envy?♪

43:22.391 --> 43:24.870
♪Let me lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

43:24.871 --> 43:29.190
♪To adorn your hair with a jade hairpin♪

43:29.191 --> 43:31.380
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms♪

43:31.381 --> 43:35.831
♪Bloom in a single night for you♪

43:35.981 --> 43:39.110
♪The splendor of the world is
but fleeting sorrow♪

43:39.111 --> 43:42.201
♪Should the flames of war arise♪

43:42.541 --> 43:45.790
♪I shall hold your hand♪

43:45.791 --> 43:48.770
♪And walk through the dust♪

43:48.771 --> 43:50.980
♪I want to hold you in my arms♪

43:50.981 --> 43:55.270
♪Leaving the world behind♪

43:55.271 --> 43:57.580
♪From now on,
all the vast wonders of the world♪

43:57.581 --> 44:01.830
♪May be left as blank spaces♪

44:01.831 --> 44:05.531
♪The dazzling spring moon over the city♪

44:05.711 --> 44:08.771
♪Is no match for your beauty♪

44:08.941 --> 44:14.151
♪Why ascend to high towers again?♪

44:14.951 --> 44:17.210
♪I will lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

44:17.211 --> 44:18.850
♪Break my spear to crown you♪

44:18.851 --> 44:21.570
♪With a golden-branch hairpin♪

44:21.571 --> 44:23.690
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms♪

44:23.691 --> 44:27.800
♪Bloom for you♪

44:27.801 --> 44:31.561
♪No more guarding lonely towers♪

44:31.601 --> 44:34.920
♪Spring is near, ripe for the taking♪

44:34.921 --> 44:36.260
♪Holding your hand♪

44:36.261 --> 44:41.211
♪Till we reach beyond the noise♪

44:41.651 --> 44:44.801
♪Only for you, I shall paint♪

44:44.991 --> 44:47.781
♪With bold strokes and vibrant colors♪

44:47.971 --> 44:49.820
♪And for all else♪

44:49.821 --> 44:56.811
♪Let it remain pale and void♪

44:59.351 --> 45:00.390
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama.)

45:00.391 --> 45:01.390
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:01.391 --> 45:02.571
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home.)
